{"tid":467122,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Iphone 用家注意 可以睇睇","createTime":"2017-11-13T08:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T20:50:55.000Z","uid":15693,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf0ea4efcb39a15daa489b976df1a89d705babe","tid":467122,"uid":15693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"近期見到好多人原來係唔識預約Iphone 個維修服務<br />\n有好多人係打上去叫人幫你約 有人係用電腦約<br />\n其實唔洗咁麻煩<br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n首先去app store<br />\n下載一個叫<br />\nApple support<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/161837_5df35f6dd4cda56b32aad1ce4cae3913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F161837_5df35f6dd4cda56b32aad1ce4cae3913.jpg&h=09421b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後打開佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/162032_bce2a8278497513ceece5f206a818ec7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F162032_bce2a8278497513ceece5f206a818ec7.jpg&h=4bab6289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後點翻你嘅電話<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/162138_c3d9f569c2b72c568b529633fdec50dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F162138_c3d9f569c2b72c568b529633fdec50dd.jpg&h=a33a794f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵翻你嘅問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/162217_7a52dab198bce5879c983bf7f7333bb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F162217_7a52dab198bce5879c983bf7f7333bb9.jpg&h=7c18b8a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/162234_fd8281d52da13eddc6aea376df22a35f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F162234_fd8281d52da13eddc6aea376df22a35f.jpg&h=70b63792&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/162242_8cc3be85f25399db5804e4693054cbf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F162242_8cc3be85f25399db5804e4693054cbf2.jpg&h=f5bc4513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後搵埋你想要嘅地點同時間就可以去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後可能好多人識 識嘅就繼續用<br />\n唔識嘅人希望可以幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82eaac9f223b428f9a880c71c14c75002deb4cfc","tid":467122,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77703d4e96671f681763074fd52c72a42930333f","tid":467122,"uid":117458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b303c5ed1d46b230597e8bae50c2d890fca22544","tid":467122,"uid":148201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30cab8ecadd723f1ef9a938871fcf1f07a4dc8a","tid":467122,"uid":67009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c619b80744cf7d2d7a9bbecf6cfaa60803ba27c5","tid":467122,"uid":22869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/162905_c27fa042376718807b65c0076103a743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F162905_c27fa0423